  <!-- EN: Rules use method:
The format of a rule is: key->text.
Text can be specified using the [key] to indicate that the text here is the text that the key refers to. If the key has multiple corresponding texts, a random one will be selected during generation.
When editing quest text, you can also use [the key of the object] to obtain the corresponding text of the object.
The rules are applied in different places, requiring different keys to output the final text.
For example, when rules are used for quest names, questName is required to output the final text. For more details, please refer to examples provided in this mod.

Here are some key requirements:

QuestName: questName-> 
QuestDescription: questDescription->
SiteName: SiteName-> -->
  <RuleTip>文本集食用方法：\n  文本集由许多个规则构成\n  一条规则的格式为：键 -> 文本\n  文本可以使用[键]来指定这里的文本是匙所指代的文本，若匙有多个对应文本，则生成时随机选择一条文本。\n  编辑任务文本时也可以用[事物的密匙]来获取该事物对应的文本。\n  然后规则在不同的地方被运用需要不同的键来输出最终文本。\n  例如：规则用于任务名字时需要用questName来输出最终文本，详细可以看本mod自带的示例。\n  以下是一些地方需要的键：\n  任务名字 -> questName\n  任务描述 -> questDescription\n  站点名字 -> SiteName</RuleTip>

