  <!-- EN: Used for outputting signals.
Each pawn will output a tag when executing events such as being killed or injured [DataName] [Number] The signal of behavior (in fact, the relevant task number is added at the beginning to identify which task needs to receive the signal).
The number is assigned according to the generation order when generating all entities of this data, starting from 0. For example, if a total of ten entities are generated, the fifth generated number is 4
If a map is generated with a data name of "HaiLuan", the fifth spawned pawn will emit a signal of "HaiLuan.4.Killed" when she is killed,
When spawned from the LootBox, [label] is the name of the loot box.If not, it means none and will not have a '.' after the label.

The following is a list of behaviors and signals corresponding to each other:
ChangeFaction
Change faction and the new faction is not a player faction: ChangedFactionToNonPlayer
Change faction and the new faction is a player faction: ChangedFactionToPlayer
When generating pawn: Spawned
When the pawn is destroyed: Despawned
When an pawn is killed: Killed
Suffer damage from player faction: TookDamageFromPlayer
Leaving Map: LeftMap

When spawning, the spawned pawn will be recorded in the "quest database", and its "key" is its data name -->
  <PawnDataNameTip>用于输出信号。\n  每个实体执行被杀死或受伤时等等事件时就会输出[标签].[数据名称].[编号].[行为]的信号（实际上最前面会加相关任务的编号以识别是哪个任务需要接受的信号，但你本身不用填写）。\n  其中编号是在生成这个数据的所有实体时，根据生成顺序赋予的，从0开始，如一共生成十个实体，第五个生成的编号为4\n  如一个生成地图时生成的，数据名称为骸鸾的，第五个生成的实体被杀死时会发出[骸鸾.4.Kiied]的信号，\n  由战利品箱(LootBox)生成时，[标签]为战利品箱的名字，若不是则为无，同时不会具有标签后的“.”。\n  以下是行为与信号对应列表：\n  改变派系：ChangedFaction\n  改变派系且新派系不是玩家派系：ChangedFactionToNonPlayer\n  改变派系且新派系是玩家派系：ChangedFactionToPlayer\n  实体生成时：Spawned\n  实体被摧毁时：Despawned\n  实体被杀死时：Killed\n  受到来自玩家派系的伤害：TookDamageFromPlayer\n  离开地图：LeftMap\n  \n  在生成时，会将生成的实体记录到“任务数据库”中，其“密匙”则是其数据名字</PawnDataNameTip>
